{"comments":"QR Code Pattern Placement — Finder, timing, alignment, and format areas.\n\n## Pattern Types\n\n1. **Finder patterns** — 7×7 patterns in three corners (TL, TR, BL)\n2. **Separators** — 1-module white border around finders\n3. **Timing patterns** — Alternating dark/light from finder to finder\n4. **Alignment patterns** — 5×5 patterns (version 2+)\n5. **Format/version areas** — Reserved for encoding metadata\n\n## Alignment Pattern Positions\n\nEach QR version (2-40) has specific alignment pattern center positions\ndefined in ISO 18004. Version 1 has no alignment patterns.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Initialize empty matrix for a version.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Types","Version"],"QRVersion"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Types","Matrix"],"QRMatrix"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[73,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/Patterns.purs","start":[73,1]},"title":"initializeMatrix"},{"children":[],"comments":"Place the three finder patterns in corners.\n\nFinder patterns are 7x7 with structure:\n███████\n█░░░░░█\n█░███░█\n█░███░█\n█░███░█\n█░░░░░█\n███████\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Types","Matrix"],"QRMatrix"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","QRCode","Types","Matrix"],"QRMatrix"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,44],"name":"../../hydroge